	  be displayed in the entry fields.

2004-06-28  MenTaLguY  <mental@rydia.net>

	* src/xml/repr-action.cpp, src/xml/repr-action.h, src/xml/repr-css.cpp,
	  src/xml/repr-io.cpp, src/xml/repr-private.h, src/xml/repr-util.cpp,
