	  is.

2004-06-26  Carl Hetherington  <inkscape@carlh.net>

	* src/node-context.cpp: make sure nodepath->nodeContext is set up
	when the selection changes.  Fixes 936739.

2004-06-25  MenTaLguY  <mental@rydia.net>

