	  from *_CPPFLAGS.

	* src/*/makefile.in: `%' as a target doesn't behave as intended,
	so replace with less general `clean %.a %.o' and add .SUFFIXES.

2004-04-22  Ted Gould  <ted@gould.cx>

	* src/draw-context.cpp, src/dropper-context.cpp,
